{"lastModified":1770324598536,"uri":"c::10217414183::vessel::c53a1cb0-02a7-11f1-8cf5-6d048875540f","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nExperience Space and Freedom while cruising on the Bali 4.6, the Luxury 46-foot catamaran by Bali.\n\nDesigned for long-term voyages, the Bali 4.6 catamaran offers 95 m² of comfort and space, with a design by Piaton&Bercault. The huge Open Space accommodates a U-shaped galley, a saloon for 10 guests and a very large sofa. A dream at sea for your faraway destinations!\n\nThe Bali 4.6 is instantly recognisable thanks to the design of its hulls, with their slender, straight bows and elegant lines drawn by Xavier Faÿ. This 46-footer benefits from all the innovations designed by Catana Group and Olivier Poncin, which are part of the DNA of Bali, along with the experience of the Catana brand. The interior design is by Agence Berco design + Piaton.","blueprint":{"name":"DREAM ON","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::c53a1cb0-02a7-11f1-8cf5-6d048875540f::assets::d86c7b40-02aa-11f1-88f3-e3ad0c4e072b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c53a1cb0-02a7-11f1-8cf5-6d048875540f::assets::d86a0a40-02aa-11f1-88f3-e3ad0c4e072b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c53a1cb0-02a7-11f1-8cf5-6d048875540f::assets::d85c0080-02aa-11f1-9a05-5d165a51ca64/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c53a1cb0-02a7-11f1-8cf5-6d048875540f::assets::d85c75b0-02aa-11f1-88f3-e3ad0c4e072b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c53a1cb0-02a7-11f1-8cf5-6d048875540f::assets::d868f8d0-02aa-11f1-9a05-5d165a51ca64/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c53a1cb0-02a7-11f1-8cf5-6d048875540f::assets::d85e9890-02aa-11f1-88f3-e3ad0c4e072b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c53a1cb0-02a7-11f1-8cf5-6d048875540f::assets::d85e4a70-02aa-11f1-88f3-e3ad0c4e072b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c53a1cb0-02a7-11f1-8cf5-6d048875540f::assets::d85d6010-02aa-11f1-88f3-e3a